---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import { bookingUrl, faqs, servicePaths, services } from '../data/services';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Soul Clarity & Spiritual Companionship | Pondering Silver"
  description="1:1 sessions for honest reflection, pattern recognition, spiritual companionship, and reconnection with inner guidance."
>
  <article class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-14 pr-16 sm:pr-0 2xl:max-w-4xl">
    <header class="space-y-6 text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-purple-700">
        1:1 reflective work
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">Soul Clarity &amp; Spiritual Companionship</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        A judgment-free space for honest reflection, pattern recognition, and reconnection with your own inner guidance.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
      <div class="space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
        <p>
          You do not need to arrive with a clear question or a polished explanation. You can bring the part of your life
          that feels tangled, painful, repetitive, uncertain, contradictory, or difficult to speak about. We begin with
          what is actually present.
        </p>
        <p>
          As you speak, I listen not only to the events you describe, but to the patterns beneath them: where attention
          keeps returning, where something tightens, what remains unsaid, which beliefs are shaping your experience, and
          where you may already know something that you have not yet allowed yourself to trust.
        </p>
        <p>
          I may ask questions, reflect patterns, challenge an interpretation, offer another way of seeing, or simply stay
          with you while something becomes clearer. The work is collaborative and responsive, not a fixed method or
          script.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="rounded-lg border border-purple-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-xs">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800">The center of the work</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          My intention is not to tell you who to become, impose my spiritual beliefs, or make your decisions for you. It
          is to help create the conditions in which you can hear yourself more clearly and reconnect with the deeper
          intelligence, integrity, and inner Light already present within you.
        </p>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Choose the Shape</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          The work is one living conversation. These are the two simplest ways to enter it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
        {servicePaths.map((path) => (
          <div class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-xs transition hover:border-purple-200 hover:shadow-md">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-purple-700">{path.rhythm}</p>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">{path.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 flex-1 leading-relaxed text-gray-600">{path.description}</p>
            <a
              href={bookingUrl}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 self-start rounded-lg bg-purple-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-xs transition hover:bg-purple-700 hover:text-white focus:outline-hidden focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-purple-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
            >
              <Icon name="heroicons:calendar-days" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" />
              <span>Schedule a Session</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">What May Arise</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          You do not have to choose the perfect doorway. These are common threads that may appear inside a session or
          over ongoing work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4">
        {services.map((service) => (
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-purple-500 bg-white p-6 shadow-xs">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800">{service.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-600">{service.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid gap-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-xs sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="flex gap-3">
        <Icon name="heroicons:heart" class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-purple-600" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Warmth without collusion</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            You will be met with care, but not with automatic agreement if a familiar story seems to be keeping you
            trapped.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
        <Icon name="heroicons:sparkles" class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-purple-600" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Spiritual when it is natural</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            Meditation, prayer, energy, and mystical language can enter the work when they are useful and welcome.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
        <Icon name="heroicons:chat-bubble-left-right" class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-purple-600" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Organic conversation</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            There is no script to perform. We follow the living thread of what is happening in you now.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
        <Icon name="heroicons:light-bulb" class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-purple-600" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Your knowing stays central</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            The aim is not dependency on my insight, but clearer contact with your own discernment and inner Light.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-purple-100 bg-purple-50 p-8 text-center shadow-xs">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-gray-700">
        Sessions are individualized around what is actually happening in your experience, with room for honesty,
        tenderness, challenge, silence, and clarity.
      </p>
      <a
        href={bookingUrl}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-purple-600 px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white shadow-xs transition hover:bg-purple-700 hover:text-white focus:outline-hidden focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-purple-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
      >
        <Icon name="heroicons:arrow-right" class="h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
        <span>Book Your Session</span>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        {faqs.map((faq) => (
          <details class="group overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-xs">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-4 text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 transition-colors duration-200 group-open:bg-gray-50">
              <span class="flex-1">{faq.question}</span>
              <span class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5 group-open:hidden">
                  <path d="M12 4a1 1 0 011 1v6h6a1 1 0 110 2h-6v6a1 1 0 11-2 0v-6H5a1 1 0 110-2h6V5a1 1 0 011-1z" />
                </svg>
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="hidden h-5 w-5 group-open:block">
                  <path d="M5 11a1 1 0 100 2h14a1 1 0 100-2H5z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-100 px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">
              {faq.answer}
            </div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  details summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }
</style>
